metadata.name: HappyLand Map
metadata.description:
Art Collectibles + Music-empowered NFTs. 
Series II Gummy Bears will consist of 100 Special  1 of 1 NFTs comprised of the original 20 HappyLand bears dens. 

5 bears, in turn, will be minted from a different bear den every 2-4 weeks and will airdrop to original HappyLand Gummy Bear holders, be won through giveaways or auctioned until completed.

Each NFT will grant owners claimable airdrops of music samples packs, Exclusive art NFTs, raffles entries, bear scat and more in the future.
